function FadeIn({children,delay=0,d="up"}) { const[v,setV]=useState(false); useEffect(()=>{const t=setTimeout(()=>setV(true),delay);return()=>clearTimeout(t);},[delay]); const tr=d==="up"?"translateY(16px)":d==="right"?"translateX(16px)":"translateY(-16px)"; return <div style={{opacity:v?1:0,transform:v?"none":tr,transition:`all 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) ${delay}ms`}}>{children}</div>; }

function Confetti({active}) { if(!active)return null; const ps=Array.from({length:40},(_,i)=>({id:i,x:Math.random()*100,dl:Math.random()*0.6,cl:["#fbbf24","#3b82f6","#10b981","#f87171","#a78bfa","#f59e0b"][i%6],sz:4+Math.random()*6,dur:1.5+Math.random()*1.5,dr:-30+Math.random()*60})); return <div style={{position:"fixed",top:0,left:0,right:0,bottom:0,pointerEvents:"none",zIndex:9999,overflow:"hidden"}}><style>{`@keyframes cF{0%{transform:translateY(-20px) rotate(0);opacity:1}100%{transform:translateY(100vh) rotate(720deg);opacity:0}}`}</style>{ps.map(p=><div key={p.id} style={{position:"absolute",top:-10,left:`${p.x}%`,width:p.sz,height:p.sz*1.4,borderRadius:p.sz>7?"50%":1,background:p.cl,animation:`cF ${p.dur}s ease-out ${p.dl}s forwards`,transform:`translateX(${p.dr}px)`}}/>)}</div>; }

